			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Load SCL_Main_A, run debug command \"oe Oubliette_Enter\" and walk towards the upper area of the Oubliette (trigger at 687.933; -33.278; -53.106). This will play once per user and nearby players.\r\nTo set the \"seen hook horrors\" flag, select the desired character with Ctrl+Shift+LeftClick and run ReCon command \"SetCharacterOsirisFlag UND_HookHorrors_Knows_SeenHookHorrors\", then use the commands above. To reset the Oubliette dialogs, use \"oe Oubliette_Reset\"."
				},
